	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ago tibi immensas gratias pro rebus, quas in literis tuis inveni; non negligens ero in rependenda vicissitudine.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ibiscum civitatem nostri traditam et <persName type="auto_name">baronem de Mansfeld</persName> captum, qui volebat impressione facta evadere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc <placeName type="citizen_name">Avene</placeName> a <placeName type="citizen_name">Gallo</placeName> oppugnati <placeName type="auto_name">Caesareani</placeName> timore sunt perculsi, fugiunt aut se dedunt, quum nihi auxilii a Cęsare sperant.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Martinus de Rossa</persName> fugit; aiunt illum esse <placeName ref="l168" cert="high">Gandavi</placeName> in arce.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Regina Bruxellę</persName> est, ad fugam paratissima.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francofordia</placeName> est obsessa ab <persName type="auto_name">Alberto</persName> marchione et <persName ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauritio</persName>; coniunxerunt enim exercitus, ne quid insperatum accidat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Hessus</persName> conqueritur se magnum accepisse damnum et ab illis, qui ab eo nunquam laesi fuere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De Turca hęc a d.  <persName type="auto_name">Lazio</persName> habemus: Turca magnum in <placeName type="auto_name">Transsylvanos</placeName> et nos exercitum mittit; sed rex Transsylvaniam tribus Germanorum legionibus et una <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName>, item <placeName type="auto_name">Hungarorum</placeName> 18 millibus firmavit, ut sine periculo esse possit contra omnes Turcicos conatus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882" cert="high">Hungaria</placeName> sparsim sunt Germani, Itali ac Hungari numero 30 millia, congregantur adhuc plura.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Rex Ferdinandus</persName> vocatur ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882" cert="high">Hungaris</placeName>, qui propediem instructo exercitu, quem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2449" cert="high">Bohemia</placeName> collegit, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcę</placeName> obviam iturus est et prostraturus omnes illius copias.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc ille.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic videmus <placeName type="auto_name">Germaniam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name">Belgas</placeName>, <placeName type="auto_name">Austriam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name">Transylvaniam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name">Neapolitanum</placeName> regnum, imo totam fere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2536" cert="high">Europam</placeName> turbulentissimam esse.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed pauci reperiuntur tam ex regibus quam principibus, qui emendent vitam, religionem sanam instituant et deum ex cordis affectu invocant et colant.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc paucis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mittam brevi libros, quos petis, si ullo modo possum adsequi.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinam</placeName>, sed responsum nullum accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Protoscriba respondebit pro se.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quidam ex militibus... e castris <persName type="auto_name">Galli</persName>... redeunt infirmi, laceri <foreign xml:lang="el">και αψρηματοι</foreign> neque possunt ferre aestum et labores bellicos.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tumultus fere excitatus fuit a paganis nostris, qui noluerunt attingere <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName> terras; sed subscripserunt civitatum consilia.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">20. iulii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Io[annes] Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pio et docto viro d. magistro <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, pastori apud <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinam</placeName> ecclesiam vigilantissimo, praeceptori suo charissimo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
